### POST /api/v1/trips/{id}/accept
### Descripción: Conductor acepta el viaje. Requiere rol Driver o Admin.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TripDto) | 403 | 404 | 422 (invalid transition, etc.)

# @name acceptTrip
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "{{VEHICLE_ID}}"
}

### Response esperado (200): TripDto
### Response error (422): DRIVER_NOT_ASSIGNED, INVALID_TRANSITION, etc.
